Interface PsyFormalStream<T extends PsyObject>

All Superinterfaces:
PsyCloseable, PsyConcatenable<PsyFormalStream<T>>, PsyObject, PsySequential<T>, PsyStreamable<T>
All Known Implementing Classes:
PsyRange, PsyStream
@Type("formalstream") public interface PsyFormalStream<T extends PsyObject> extends PsyStreamable<T>, PsyCloseable, PsyConcatenable<PsyFormalStream<T>>
The representation of formalstream, an abstraction of the stream.
